Marks & Spencer Same-Store Merchandise Sales Fall 3.9% in Fourth Quarter

-- B y   J e r r o l d   C o l t e n
-- 
2011-04-06T06:02:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-06/marks-spencer-same-store-merchandise-sales-fall-3-9-in-fourth-quarter.html
Marks & Spencer Group Plc (MKS)  said in a
statement today that group sales rose 2.3 percent in the fourth
quarter.  Quarterly like-for-like sales for U.K. general merchandise
were down 3.9 percent, compared with an estimate of a 6 percent
decline.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jerrold Colten at 
 jcolten@bloomberg.net  